OL,4,Crefunds because of ongoing 'technical
OL,5,Cissue'
OL,7,FSouthern Railway say some passengers
OL,8,Fwill be receiving refunds after being
OL,9,Fovercharged because of a 'technical
OL,10,Fissue'.
OL,12,FThe company says a small number of its
OL,13,Fcustomers are affected by an ongoing
OL,14,Fglitch at stations where the option to
OL,15,Ftravel using contactless payments was
OL,16,Fintroduced last month.
OL,18,FFrom December 14th, the payment method
OL,19,Fwas introduced at an additional 11
OL,20,Fstations on the network including East
OL,21,FGrinstead, Oxted and Reigate.
