OL,7,FThe Rail Delivery Group said the
OL,8,Fexpansion of pay-as-you-go technology
OL,9,Fis designed to make train travel
OL,10,Feasier and more convenient, aligning
OL,11,Fit with the Transport for London
OL,12,Fnetwork.
OL,14,FRefunds for journeys impacted since
OL,15,Fthe middle of last month will be
OL,16,Fissued automatically by Transport for
OL,17,FLondon from Monday 5th January.
