OL,7,FIn a statement on its website,
OL,8,FSouthern Railway says, "TfL have begun
OL,9,Fissuing refunds for affected journeys
OL,10,Fas part of interim arrangements.
OL,11,FPassengers can expect to begin seeing
OL,12,Frefunds applied to their accounts
OL,13,Fshortly, and refunds will continue to
OL,14,Fbe processed on a weekly basis while
OL,15,Fthe issue remains in place.
