OL,7,F"If you think you may have been
OL,8,Fovercharged, you can review up to
OL,9,Fseven days of journey history and
OL,10,Fcharges by setting up an account on
OL,11,Fthe TfL website, which also provides
OL,12,Fadditional useful features. To check
OL,13,Fthe charge applied against the correct
OL,14,Ffare, you can compare your journey
OL,15,Fdetails on National Rail Enquiries.
