OL,5,Cissue'
OL,7,F"We are working with TfL on a
OL,8,Fpermanent fix. However, changes to
OL,9,Faddress this issue can only be
OL,10,Fimplemented as part of a wider 'Fare
OL,11,FSetting Round', with the next one
OL,12,Fscheduled for March 2026. In the
OL,13,Fmeantime, we are ensuring that all
OL,14,Ffares data for pay as you go with
OL,15,Fcontactless journeys is accurate and
OL,16,Ffully verified before release.
OL,17,FAdditional checks and testing will
OL,18,Falso be carried out to prevent this
OL,19,Fissue from recurring.
