OL,7,F"Passengers travelling from some
OL,8,Fstations may currently be undercharged
OL,9,Fwhen using pay as you go with
OL,10,Fcontactless. You will not be asked to
OL,11,Fpay any extra for past or current
OL,12,Fjourneys. From March onwards, fares
OL,13,Fwill be charged at the correct rate."
